precis:
Authority to enter into a CONTRIBUTION AGREEMENT with the Government of
the NORTHWEST TERRITORIES for the implementation of NATIONAL SAFETY CODE
STANDARD NO. 14 (COMPLIANCE REVIEW - SAFETY RATING), a standard that
ascribes a safety performance rating to all truck and bus carriers.
